full_text: IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE FIFTEENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA GRAND JUROR'S SUBPOENA TO: [REDACTED] YOU ARE HEREBY COMMANDED to be and appear before the Grand Jury of the Circuit Court for the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit of the State of Florida, in Room 4-A, Juvenile Court's Building, Palm Beach County Courthouse, 205 North Dixie Highway, West Palm Beach, Florida, on 07/19/2006, at 9:00 AM, to testify and the truth to speak in behalf of the State of Florida, in a certain matter before the Grand Jury empaneled and sworn to inquire in and for the body of Palm Beach County, and herein fail not under penalty of the law. WITNESS, The Honorable Circuit Court, as also SHARON R. BOCK, Clerk and the Seal of said Court, at the Courthouse in West Palm Beach, Florida on July 14, 2006. By: Deputy Clerk LANNA BELOHLAVEK Fla. Bar #0776726 Assistant State Attorney Received this subpoena on the 14 day of July 2006, and executed the same on the 17 day of July 2006, by delivering a True Copy thereof to the within named witness in the County of Palm Beach, State of Florida. RIC L. BRADSHAW, SHERIFF By: Deputy Sheriff If you are a person with a disability who needs any accommodation in order to participate in this proceeding, you are entitled, at no cost to you, to the provision of certain assistance. Please contact the ADA Coordinator in the Administrative Office of the Court, Palm Beach County Courthouse, 205 North Dixie Highway, Room 5.2500, West Palm Beach, Florida, 33401; telephone number (561) 355-4380 within two (2) working days of your receipt of this notice; if you are hearing or voice impaired, call 1-800-955-8771. SERVED TIME 7:10A M. DATE 7/17/06 COMMENT NOT SERVED Page 107 of 124 Public Records Request No. 172295 SERVING PROCESS DOJ-OGR-00031828

text_blocks.content: IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE FIFTEENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA GRAND JUROR'S SUBPOENA

organizations: Circuit Court of the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit

additional_notes: The document is a Grand Juror's Subpoena issued by the Circuit Court of the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit in Palm Beach County, Florida. It is dated July 14, 2006, and requires the recipient to appear before the Grand Jury on July 19, 2006. The document contains handwritten notes and signatures, including the signature of the Deputy Clerk and the Deputy Sheriff. The document also includes a stamp indicating that it was served on July 17, 2006, at 7:10 AM.
